@node "Iconize"

@toc "Edit menu"

@{U}1.3.9  Iconize [F5]                                    PHOENIX Manager@{u}



When you activate this menu entry (or its equivalent in the function

key bar) the topped window will be converted to an icon. You can

perform some operations with the icon (see Icon operations in the

@{"The Manager's desktop" LINK "Schreibtisch des Managers"} description).



If the topped window is a @{"table window" LINK "Tabellen-Fenster"} or a @{"process window" LINK "Prozeû-Fenster"}, then this

