@autorefon

     menu entry). In that case the saving performs the same as the

     @{"Insert" LINK "Insert (record)"} command. After this the contents of the mask will be

     cleared, so that you can compose a new data record; this can be

     switched off in the @{"Configure masks" LINK "Dialogbox Masken-Konfiguration"} command of the Manager's

     Parameters menu.

