the Process menu (or its equivalent in the function key bar), as well

as the Open command as long as a data record in a report-list window

is selected during this.



The window's title line shows the name of the report. If the report

has not been saved yet, it will display <Unnamed>.



For certain actions the info line below this will display coordinates

