possible to drag a table, a @{"table icon" LINK "Tabellen-Sinnbild"} or individual data records from a

a @{"table window" LINK "Tabellen-Fenster"} directly into the report window and drop them there.

The effect of this is that the report in this window will be executed

with these data records. The report window need not necessarily be

topped for this.



First a preview of the report will be displayed in a @{"preview window" LINK "Vorschau-Fenster"}.

If you are satisfied with the result, you can start a printout with

the File/Print menu entry, or by clicking on the Printer icon in the

Manager icon bar.



If you want to print immediately and skip the preview, then if the

report window is active you can click on the Printer icon straight

away, or use File/Print.



@endnode





