only three places defined in the format for a numeric field, then this

field can only display a maximum of three places, i.e. numbers up to

999. In the case of an overflow the numbers will be replaced by the

character '#', just as in table windows. This is because the sum also

uses the same format. IN that case the default format should be over-

written as described above.



