In the character-string @{B}String@{b} the characters of @{B}pattern@{b} will be

replaced by the character-string specified under @{B}replacement@{b} and

the result assigned to the field or variable @{B}Result@{b}.



@{I}Example:@{i}

Result=REPLACE("Meyer", "ey", "ai");



@{B}Result@{b} then contains: Maier



